---
title:          "Homework is teamwork: Experimental evidence on parental involvement in education in Uganda"
date:           2024-010-07 00:01:00 +0800
# selected:       true
type:           "Work in Progress"
# pub:            "PEDL"
# pub_pre:        "Submitted"
# pub_post:       'Under review.'
pub_last:       "(Draft in preparation)"
pub_date:       "2025"

abstract: >-
  We provide households in Uganda with educational material and an action plan for their primary-school child. We find increased time mothers spend on learning activities with their child and increased exam registration, particularly for children from low-income families.
